kernel/watchdog: fix watchdog_allowed_mask not used warning

Define watchdog_allowed_mask only when SOFTLOCKUP_DETECTOR is enabled.

Fixes: 7feeb9cd4f5b ("watchdog/sysctl: Clean up sysctl variable name space")
